---
import { BOOKING_URL } from '../config';
---
<section id="what-you-get" class="w-full max-w-[1200px] px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-24 md:py-32 z-20 relative scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="relative">
        <div class="reveal-text mb-4">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest">What you get</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-6 reveal-text">
            What's Inside AI Amplify Academy
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
            <!-- Feature 1: 7 Money-Making AI Courses -->
            <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-purple-500/20 transition-colors reveal-text">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-4">
                    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">The 7 Money-Making AI Courses</h3>
                    <span class="text-purple-400 font-mono text-sm">Value: $2,997</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm sm:text-base mb-4">Complete step-by-step training on the AI skills that actually pay:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-300 text-sm sm:text-base mb-4">
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> AI Freelancing Blueprint: How to find clients, pitch services, and close deals</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> Building AI Apps for Profit: Create and sell AI-powered tools (no coding required)</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> AI Content Creation Business: Build a $3K–10K/month content service</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> AI Automation for Businesses: The #1 most in-demand (and highest-paying) AI skill</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> AI Video Production: Create professional videos in minutes and sell them</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> AI Design & Visuals: Build a graphic design business powered by AI</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> AI Backend Systems: Advanced automation for premium clients</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Each course includes: Step-by-step video lessons • Copy-paste templates and scripts • Real client examples and case studies • Pricing guides (what to charge)</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 2: Weekly Live Workshops -->
            <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-purple-500/20 transition-colors reveal-text">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-4">
                    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Weekly Live Money-Making Workshops</h3>
                    <span class="text-purple-400 font-mono text-sm">Value: $497/month</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm sm:text-base mb-3">Every week, we host live training on:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-300 text-sm sm:text-base mb-3">
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> What's working RIGHT NOW to make money with AI</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> New AI tools and how to monetize them</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> Member hot-seats (get your questions answered live)</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0">•</span> Guest experts sharing their strategies</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">All workshops are recorded so you never miss one.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 3: AI Money-Makers Community -->
            <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-purple-500/20 transition-colors reveal-text">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-4">
                    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">The AI Money-Makers Community</h3>
                    <span class="text-purple-400 font-mono text-sm">Value: Priceless</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm sm:text-base mb-3">Join 500+ people who are actively making money with AI:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-300 text-sm sm:text-base mb-4">
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Get answers to your questions in minutes (not hours)</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Share wins, strategies, and lessons learned</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Find collaboration partners and referrals</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Stay motivated and accountable</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Access to exclusive job boards and client leads</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm italic">This isn't a "course dump." This is a living, breathing community of people who are doing this every single day.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 4: Direct Access to Braydon -->
            <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-purple-500/20 transition-colors reveal-text">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 mb-4">
                    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Direct Access to Braydon</h3>
                    <span class="text-purple-400 font-mono text-sm">Value: $297/month</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm sm:text-base mb-3">Unlike other "gurus" who disappear after you buy, I'm active in the community every single day:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-300 text-sm sm:text-base mb-4">
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Ask me questions directly</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Get feedback on your projects</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Strategy help when you're stuck</li>
                    <li class="flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i> Accountability and motivation</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm">I've helped over 500 people make money with AI. I'll help you too.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Value Stack Summary -->
            <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border-2 border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-500/5 reveal-text text-center">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Value Stack Summary</h3>
                <p class="text-neutral-300 text-base sm:text-lg mb-2"><span class="text-white font-semibold">Total Value:</span> $4,288+ per month</p>
                <p class="text-purple-400 text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold">Your Investment: $30/month <span class="text-neutral-400 font-normal text-base">(or FREE with Go High Level)</span></p>
                <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm mt-2">Not sure yet? Book a free strategy call first—no obligation.</p>
                <a href={BOOKING_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mt-6 px-8 py-3.5 bg-white text-black rounded-full text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-neutral-200 transition-all">
                    Book your free strategy call
                    <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
        entries.forEach(entry => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                entry.target.classList.add('reveal-visible');
            }
        });
    }, { threshold: 0.1 });
    document.querySelectorAll('#what-you-get .reveal-text').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>
